  )
Description: Launches an interactive chat app that retrieves and
    summarizes relevant Tidymodels documentation and on-line materials
    using both semantic and keyword-based search via an OpenAI-powered
    assistant. Returns authoritative excerpts, includes links to official
    resources, and helps users accomplish specific Tidymodels tasks
    quickly.
